射出，超级巨人“凯兽王”的身体完成。适合操作超级巨人“凯兽王”的飞行员强武钻坐上“大空魔龙”并接受露露(ルル・アージェス)的教导。他乘坐在“凯兽王”, 击败怪异野兽。上尉\"格里斯\"为了保护地面，和为了抢救认为已死的父亲钻离开母亲和朋友身边，前往异世界Darrieus 。","name":"ガイキング LEGEND OF DAIKU-MARYU","name_cn":"新大空魔龙","tags":[{"name":"东映","count":32,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":31,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2005","count":29,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萝卜","count":27,"total_cont":0},{"name":"机战","count":23,"total_cont":0},{"name":"東映アニメーション","count":17,"total_cont":0},{"name":"大空魔龙","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"复刻版","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"草尾毅","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"三条陸","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"robo","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2005年11月","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科幻","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"机器人","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"田中真弓","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"川上とも子","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"作画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"手塚理","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2005年10月","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"机甲","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"喜欢","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山崎健志","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"旧物","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"阅","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补番","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"音乐×","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"新大空魔龙"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"新宇宙飞龙"},{"v":"Gaiking: Legend of Daiku-Maryu"}]},{"key":"话数","value":"39"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"2005年11月12日"},{"key":"放送星期","value":"星期六"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"http://www.toei-anim.co.jp/tv/gaiking/"},{"key":"播放电视台","value":"テレビ朝日"},{"key":"播放结束","value":"2006年9月24日"},{"key":"音乐","value":"手塚理"},{"key":"Copyright","value":"©2005 テレビ朝日・東映アニメーション"},{"key":"原案","value":"MK企画（第1話）、エムケイ（第2話～第39話）"},{"key":"系列构成","value":"三条陸"},{"key":"人物设定","value":"山崎健志、山崎展義；副人设：直井正博"},{"key":"作画监督","value":"江端里沙、直井正博、水川弘理、成